data.title: Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final Live Streaming Details: When And Where To Watch
data.meta_description: Real Madrid takes on FC Barcelona in an El Clasico Super Cup Final on Sunday in Riyadh. Here are the details.
data.text:
Spanish Super Cup Final: FC Barcelona and Real Madrid will clash in the final of the Supercopa De Espana (Spanish Super Cup) as both the teams will aim to add the first domestic silwerware in their esteemed respective trophy cabinets. Real Madrid are coming into the final on the back of an entertaining Madrid Derby in the semi final against Atletico Madrid as they defeated their fierce city rivals 5-3 after extra time.

FC Barcelona on the other hand have been playing on-and-off football this season as their dismal goalscoring records have led them to struggle in the La Liga and are finding it hard in every match to get a result. However, they saw off Osasuna with ease and entered the final with the 2-0 defeat of the La Liga club.

Barca and Real are two of the biggest clubs in the world and have given the footballing world iconic moments time and time again. The fierce rivals will be taking on each other in the Al Awal Park at King Saud University in Riyadh. The fixture is the most iconic and popular fixture in all of sports as it is the epitome of a perfect description of clash of the giants.

Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final Live Streaming Details

When is the Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final going to be held?

The Spanish Super Cup Final will be held on Sunday, January 14 and for Indian fans, it'll be on Monday, 12:30 a.m., January 15.

Where is the Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final going to be held?

The Spanish Super Cup Final will be held in the Al Awal Park at King Saud University in Riyadh.

How to watch the Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final?

The Indians fans can watch the live streaming of the Spanish Super Cup 'El Clasico' Final on the FanCode App. Unfortunately, there will be no broadcasting or telecasting of the fixture in India.
